<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta name="robots" content="noindex, nofollow">
    <title>Maintenance en cours — EntryWeb</title>
    <style>
        *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
        html { overflow-x: hidden; }

        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Arial, sans-serif;
            background: #0a0f1e;
            color: #fff;
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 40px 24px;
            overflow: hidden;
            position: relative;
        }

        /* Gradient radial d'ambiance */
        body::before {
            content: '';
            position: fixed;
            inset: 0;
            background:
                radial-gradient(ellipse 80% 60% at 50% 100%, rgba(0,102,255,0.18) 0%, transparent 70%),
                radial-gradient(ellipse 40% 30% at 80% 20%, rgba(245,158,11,0.08) 0%, transparent 60%);
            pointer-events: none;
        }

        /* Étoiles */
        .stars {
            position: fixed;
            inset: 0;
            pointer-events: none;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .star {
            position: absolute;
            width: 2px; height: 2px;
            background: #fff;
            border-radius: 50%;
            animation: twinkle var(--d, 3s) ease-in-out var(--delay, 0s) infinite;
        }
        @keyframes twinkle {
            0%, 100% { opacity: 0.2; transform: scale(1); }
            50%       { opacity: 1;   transform: scale(1.4); }
        }

        /* Logo */
        .logo {
            margin-bottom: 3rem;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }
        .logo img {
            height: 40px;
            width: auto;
            filter: brightness(0) invert(1);
        }

        /* Scène SVG */
        .scene {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
            margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
            filter: drop-shadow(0 20px 40px rgba(0,102,255,0.2));
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 420px;
        }
        .scene svg {
            width: 100%;
            height: auto;
        }

        /* Texte */
        .content {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
            text-align: center;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 1rem;
        }

        .badge {
            display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;
            background: rgba(245,158,11,0.12);
            border: 1px solid rgba(245,158,11,0.35);
            color: #fbbf24;
            font-size: 11px; font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: 0.14em; text-transform: uppercase;
            padding: 7px 16px; border-radius: 20px;
        }
        .badge-dot {
            width: 6px; height: 6px;
            border-radius: 50%; background: #fbbf24;
            box-shadow: 0 0 6px #fbbf24;
            animation: pulse 1.5s ease-in-out infinite;
        }
        @keyframes pulse {
            0%, 100% { opacity: 1; box-shadow: 0 0 6px #fbbf24; }
            50%       { opacity: 0.4; box-shadow: 0 0 2px #fbbf24; }
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: clamp(28px, 5vw, 48px);
            font-weight: 700;
            line-height: 1.15;
            letter-spacing: -0.02em;
        }
        h1 .accent {
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #0066ff, #38bdf8);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            background-clip: text;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
            line-height: 1.75;
            max-width: 400px;
        }

        /* Barre de progression animée */
        .progress-wrap {
            width: 240px;
            margin-top: 0.5rem;
        }
        .progress-label {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            font-size: 11px;
            color: rgba(255,255,255,0.35);
            margin-bottom: 6px;
            letter-spacing: 0.06em;
        }
        .progress-bar {
            height: 3px;
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
            border-radius: 10px;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .progress-fill {
            height: 100%;
            width: 0%;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #0066ff, #38bdf8);
            border-radius: 10px;
            animation: load 4s cubic-bezier(0.4,0,0.2,1) forwards;
        }
        @keyframes load {
            0%   { width: 0%; }
            30%  { width: 45%; }
            60%  { width: 68%; }
            85%  { width: 82%; }
            100% { width: 82%; }
        }

        .divider {
            width: 1px; height: 32px;
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
            margin: 0.5rem 0;
        }

        .contact {
            font-size: 13px;
            color: rgba(255,255,255,0.3);
        }
        .contact a {
            color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6);
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: color 0.2s;
        }
        .contact a:hover { color: #fff; }

        /* Sol chantier */
        .ground {
            position: fixed;
            bottom: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
            height: 8px;
            background: repeating-linear-gradient(
                90deg,
                #f59e0b 0px, #f59e0b 40px,
                #1a1a1a 40px, #1a1a1a 80px
            );
            opacity: 0.7;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <!-- Étoiles générées -->
    <div class="stars">
        <div class="star" style="top:8%;left:15%;--d:2.8s;--delay:0s"></div>
        <div class="star" style="top:12%;left:72%;--d:3.5s;--delay:0.5s;width:3px;height:3px"></div>
        <div class="star" style="top:5%;left:40%;--d:2.2s;--delay:1s"></div>
        <div class="star" style="top:20%;left:88%;--d:4s;--delay:0.3s"></div>
        <div class="star" style="top:3%;left:58%;--d:3.1s;--delay:1.5s;width:3px;height:3px"></div>
        <div class="star" style="top:15%;left:25%;--d:2.6s;--delay:0.8s"></div>
        <div class="star" style="top:25%;left:5%;--d:3.8s;--delay:0.2s"></div>
        <div class="star" style="top:7%;left:92%;--d:2.4s;--delay:1.2s"></div>
        <div class="star" style="top:18%;left:50%;--d:3.2s;--delay:0.6s"></div>
        <div class="star" style="top:30%;left:78%;--d:2.9s;--delay:1.8s"></div>
        <div class="star" style="top:10%;left:33%;--d:3.6s;--delay:0.4s;width:3px;height:3px"></div>
        <div class="star" style="top:22%;left:62%;--d:2.3s;--delay:1.1s"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="logo"><img src="/images/logo.png" alt="EntryWeb"></div>

    <!-- Scène SVG : skyline + grue -->
    <div class="scene">
        <svg width="420" height="240" viewBox="0 0 420 240" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">

            <!-- Lune -->
            <circle cx="360" cy="38" r="22" fill="#1e293b" stroke="#334155" stroke-width="1"/>
            <circle cx="370" cy="30" r="18" fill="#0a0f1e"/>

            <!-- Étoile déco -->
            <polygon points="340,18 342,24 348,24 343,28 345,34 340,30 335,34 337,28 332,24 338,24" fill="#fbbf24" opacity="0.6"/>

            <!-- Bâtiment fond gauche (petit) -->
            <rect x="10" y="160" width="45" height="80" rx="2" fill="#0f172a" stroke="#1e293b" stroke-width="1"/>
            <rect x="18" y="168" width="8" height="8" rx="1" fill="#1e3a5f" opacity="0.8"/>
            <rect x="30" y="168" width="8" height="8" rx="1" fill="#fef08a" opacity="0.7"/>
            <rect x="18" y="182" width="8" height="8" rx="1" fill="#fef08a" opacity="0.5"/>
            <rect x="30" y="182" width="8" height="8" rx="1" fill="#1e3a5f" opacity="0.8"/>
            <rect x="18" y="196" width="8" height="8" rx="1" fill="#1e3a5f" opacity="0.8"/>
            <rect x="30" y="196" width="8" height="8" rx="1" fill="#fef08a" opacity="0.7"/>

            <!-- Bâtiment fond centre -->
            <rect x="60" y="130" width="60" height="110" rx="2" fill="#0f172a" stroke="#1e293b" stroke-width="1"/>
            <rect x="68" y="140" width="10" height="10" rx="1" fill="#fef08a" opacity="0.6"/>
            <rect x="82" y="140" width="10" height="10" rx="1" fill="#1e3a5f" opacity="0.8"/>
            <rect x="96" y="140" width="10" height="10" rx="1" fill="#fef08a" opacity="0.4"/>
            <rect x="68" y="156" width="10" height="10" rx="1" fill="#1e3a5f"/>
            <rect x="82" y="156" width="10" height="10" rx="1" fill="#fef08a" opacity="0.7"/>
            <rect x="96" y="156" width="10" height="10" rx="1" fill="#1e3a5f"/>
            <rect x="68" y="172" width="10" height="10" rx="1" fill="#fef08a" opacity="0.5"/>
            <rect x="82" y="172" width="10" height="10" rx="1" fill="#1e3a5f"/>
            <rect x="96" y="172" width="10" height="10" rx="1" fill="#fef08a" opacity="0.8"/>
            <rect x="68" y="188" width="10" height="10" rx="1" fill="#1e3a5f"/>
            <rect x="82" y="188" width="10" height="10" rx="1" fill="#fef08a" opacity="0.3"/>
            <rect x="96" y="188" width="10" height="10" rx="1" fill="#fef08a" opacity="0.6"/>

            <!-- Bâtiment en construction (principal) -->
            <rect x="140" y="100" width="90" height="140" rx="2" fill="#111827" stroke="#1f2937" stroke-width="1.5"/>
            <!-- Échafaudages -->
            <line x1="140" y1="116" x2="230" y2="116" stroke="#374151" stroke-width="1.5"/>
            <line x1="140" y1="132" x2="230" y2="132" stroke="#374151" stroke-width="1.5"/>
            <line x1="140" y1="148" x2="230" y2="148" stroke="#374151" stroke-width="1.5"/>
            <line x1="162" y1="100" x2="162" y2="240" stroke="#374151" stroke-width="1"/>
            <line x1="184" y1="100" x2="184" y2="240" stroke="#374151" stroke-width="1"/>
            <line x1="206" y1="100" x2="206" y2="240" stroke="#374151" stroke-width="1"/>
            <!-- Étages en construction -->
            <rect x="140" y="100" width="90" height="16" fill="#1e293b" opacity="0.6"/>
            <!-- Fenêtres allumées -->
            <rect x="148" y="158" width="12" height="12" rx="1" fill="#0066ff" opacity="0.8"/>
            <rect x="164" y="158" width="12" height="12" rx="1" fill="#fef08a" opacity="0.6"/>
            <rect x="180" y="158" width="12" height="12" rx="1" fill="#0066ff" opacity="0.5"/>
            <rect x="196" y="158" width="12" height="12" rx="1" fill="#fef08a" opacity="0.8"/>
            <rect x="212" y="158" width="12" height="12" rx="1" fill="#1e3a5f"/>
            <rect x="148" y="176" width="12" height="12" rx="1" fill="#fef08a" opacity="0.4"/>
            <rect x="164" y="176" width="12" height="12" rx="1" fill="#1e3a5f"/>
            <rect x="180" y="176" width="12" height="12" rx="1" fill="#fef08a" opacity="0.7"/>
            <rect x="196" y="176" width="12" height="12" rx="1" fill="#0066ff" opacity="0.6"/>
            <rect x="212" y="176" width="12" height="12" rx="1" fill="#fef08a" opacity="0.5"/>
            <rect x="148" y="194" width="12" height="12" rx="1" fill="#0066ff" opacity="0.4"/>
            <rect x="164" y="194" width="12" height="12" rx="1" fill="#fef08a" opacity="0.8"/>
            <rect x="180" y="194" width="12" height="12" rx="1" fill="#1e3a5f"/>
            <rect x="196" y="194" width="12" height="12" rx="1" fill="#fef08a" opacity="0.3"/>
            <rect x="212" y="194" width="12" height="12" rx="1" fill="#0066ff" opacity="0.7"/>

            <!-- Bâtiment fond droite (grand) -->
            <rect x="260" y="80" width="55" height="160" rx="2" fill="#0f172a" stroke="#1e293b" stroke-width="1"/>
            <rect x="268" y="90" width="9" height="9" rx="1" fill="#fef08a" opacity="0.7"/>
            <rect x="281" y="90" width="9" height="9" rx="1" fill="#1e3a5f"/>
            <rect x="294" y="90" width="9" height="9" rx="1" fill="#fef08a" opacity="0.4"/>
            <rect x="268" y="105" width="9" height="9" rx="1" fill="#1e3a5f"/>
            <rect x="281" y="105" width="9" height="9" rx="1" fill="#fef08a" opacity="0.8"/>
            <rect x="294" y="105" width="9" height="9" rx="1" fill="#1e3a5f"/>
            <rect x="268" y="120" width="9" height="9" rx="1" fill="#fef08a" opacity="0.5"/>
            <rect x="281" y="120" width="9" height="9" rx="1" fill="#0066ff" opacity="0.6"/>
            <rect x="294" y="120" width="9" height="9" rx="1" fill="#fef08a" opacity="0.9"/>
            <!-- Antenne -->
            <line x1="287" y1="80" x2="287" y2="60" stroke="#374151" stroke-width="2"/>
            <circle cx="287" cy="58" r="3" fill="#ef4444">
                <animate attributeName="opacity" values="1;0.2;1" dur="1.5s" repeatCount="indefinite"/>
            </circle>

            <!-- Bâtiment fond droite (petit) -->
            <rect x="328" y="150" width="40" height="90" rx="2" fill="#0f172a" stroke="#1e293b" stroke-width="1"/>
            <rect x="336" y="158" width="8" height="8" rx="1" fill="#fef08a" opacity="0.6"/>
            <rect x="348" y="158" width="8" height="8" rx="1" fill="#1e3a5f"/>
            <rect x="336" y="172" width="8" height="8" rx="1" fill="#1e3a5f"/>
            <rect x="348" y="172" width="8" height="8" rx="1" fill="#fef08a" opacity="0.8"/>
            <rect x="336" y="186" width="8" height="8" rx="1" fill="#fef08a" opacity="0.4"/>
            <rect x="348" y="186" width="8" height="8" rx="1" fill="#1e3a5f"/>

            <!-- SOL -->
            <rect x="0" y="232" width="420" height="8" fill="#0f172a"/>
            <line x1="0" y1="232" x2="420" y2="232" stroke="#1e293b" stroke-width="1.5"/>

            <!-- ===== GRUE ===== -->
            <!-- Base / socle -->
            <rect x="372" y="220" width="36" height="12" rx="2" fill="#f59e0b"/>
            <!-- Mât vertical avec rayures sécurité -->
            <rect x="382" y="30" width="16" height="192" rx="1" fill="#f59e0b"/>
            <rect x="382" y="50" width="16" height="8" fill="#1a1a1a" opacity="0.35"/>
            <rect x="382" y="74" width="16" height="8" fill="#1a1a1a" opacity="0.35"/>
            <rect x="382" y="98" width="16" height="8" fill="#1a1a1a" opacity="0.35"/>
            <rect x="382" y="122" width="16" height="8" fill="#1a1a1a" opacity="0.35"/>
            <rect x="382" y="146" width="16" height="8" fill="#1a1a1a" opacity="0.35"/>
            <rect x="382" y="170" width="16" height="8" fill="#1a1a1a" opacity="0.35"/>
            <rect x="382" y="194" width="16" height="8" fill="#1a1a1a" opacity="0.35"/>
            <!-- Cabine opérateur -->
            <rect x="376" y="38" width="24" height="18" rx="2" fill="#d97706" stroke="#f59e0b" stroke-width="1"/>
            <rect x="380" y="42" width="8" height="8" rx="1" fill="#bae6fd" opacity="0.9"/>
            <!-- Flèche principale (longue, vers la gauche) -->
            <rect x="160" y="22" width="232" height="14" rx="3" fill="#f59e0b"/>
            <!-- Raidisseurs triangulaires -->
            <polygon points="390,22 390,36 340,36" fill="#d97706" opacity="0.6"/>
            <polygon points="390,22 390,36 260,36" fill="#d97706" opacity="0.3"/>
            <!-- Contrepoids (droite) -->
            <rect x="392" y="12" width="28" height="22" rx="3" fill="#d97706" stroke="#f59e0b" stroke-width="1.5"/>
            <!-- Feu de signalisation -->
            <circle cx="162" cy="22" r="4" fill="#ef4444">
                <animate attributeName="opacity" values="1;0.2;1" dur="1.2s" repeatCount="indefinite"/>
            </circle>

            <!-- Câble principal + crochet (animé) -->
            <g style="animation: swing 3s ease-in-out infinite; transform-origin: 220px 36px;">
                <line x1="220" y1="36" x2="220" y2="110" stroke="#94a3b8" stroke-width="2"/>
                <!-- Crochet -->
                <path d="M216 110 Q212 122 220 126 Q228 122 224 110" stroke="#94a3b8" stroke-width="2.5" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round"/>
                <!-- Charge : bloc de béton -->
                <rect x="204" y="126" width="32" height="20" rx="3" fill="#0066ff"/>
                <line x1="210" y1="132" x2="230" y2="132" stroke="rgba(255,255,255,0.25)" stroke-width="1.5"/>
                <line x1="210" y1="138" x2="224" y2="138" stroke="rgba(255,255,255,0.15)" stroke-width="1.5"/>
            </g>

            <style>
                @keyframes swing {
                    0%, 100% { transform: rotate(-5deg); }
                    50%       { transform: rotate(5deg); }
                }
            </style>

            <!-- Ouvrier sur l'immeuble -->
            <g transform="translate(148, 95)">
                <!-- Casque jaune -->
                <ellipse cx="8" cy="2" rx="7" ry="4" fill="#f59e0b"/>
                <!-- Tête -->
                <circle cx="8" cy="8" r="5" fill="#fde68a"/>
                <!-- Corps -->
                <rect x="4" y="13" width="8" height="10" rx="2" fill="#0066ff"/>
                <!-- Bras -->
                <line x1="4" y1="16" x2="-1" y2="21" stroke="#0066ff" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round"/>
                <rect x="-5" y="19" width="7" height="3" rx="1" fill="#374151" transform="rotate(-30,-5,19)"/>
                <line x1="12" y1="16" x2="16" y2="19" stroke="#0066ff" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round"/>
                <!-- Jambes -->
                <line x1="7" y1="23" x2="5" y2="30" stroke="#1e40af" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round"/>
                <line x1="11" y1="23" x2="13" y2="30" stroke="#1e40af" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round"/>
                <animateTransform attributeName="transform" type="translate" additive="sum"
                    values="0,0;0,-1;0,0" dur="1.2s" repeatCount="indefinite"/>
            </g>

        </svg>
    </div>

    <div class="content">
        <span class="badge"><span class="badge-dot"></span>Travaux en cours</span>

        <h1>On construit quelque chose<br>de <span class="accent">beau</span> pour vous</h1>

        <p>Le site est temporairement hors ligne.<br>On revient très bientôt !</p>

        <div class="progress-wrap">
            <div class="progress-label">
                <span>Mise à jour en cours</span>
                <span>82%</span>
            </div>
            <div class="progress-bar">
                <div class="progress-fill"></div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="divider"></div>

        <p class="contact">Une urgence ? <a href="mailto:contact@entryweb.fr">contact@entryweb.fr</a></p>
    </div>

    <div class="ground"></div>

</body>
</html>
